<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV119">
<l>poṉṉicūḻa raṅkamēya pūvaivaṇṇa māyakē</l>
<l>ḷeṉṉatāvi yeṉṉumvalvi ṉaiyiṉuṭko ḻunteḻun</l>
<l>tuṉṉapāta meṉṉaniṉṟa voṇcuṭarkko ḻumalar</l>
<l>maṉṉavantu pūṇṭuvāṭṭa miṉṟiyeṅku niṉṟatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O bilberry-hued [Lord] who dwell in Raṅgam surrounded by the Poṉṉi!</l>
<l rend="indent">O wonderful [Lord]! Listen:</l>
<l>[Love for You], being kindled, arose in the powerful karman that is my soul,</l>
<l>Came and dwelled on the bright, plump flowers called Your feet,</l>
<l>getting entangled [in them] and remained everywhere without withering.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
